title: review your stories with coparticipants, timely
pid: 34c57672-c463-4775-875c-1296da38fcc7
body: |2-
  On our way back from La Vega,
  reviewing the steep, messy trip down the valley to the river and dangerously back up,
  it felt right.
  Doing it later, alone, on a computer, would have felt less right.
